scopecontent.p:
The publications of SES in this collection contain a representative
		sample of the flyers, brochures, and updates prepared and distributed by the
		staff. Substantial reports, often prepared as a final product of a grant, are
		present; selected titles include 
	 Water Workshops Workbook, 1977; 
	 Water Resources of the Tortolita Area, 1977; 
	 Blue Skies: An Arizonan's Guide to Clean Air, 1980; 
	 Flood and Erosion Hazards in Tucson, 1980; and a draft of 
	 Chemicals Used in the Mining Process: Their Potential Threats to
		Ground Water, 1984.
